headline: 3 No-Brainer High-Dividend Stocks to Buy With $2,000 Right Now
summary: The S&P 500 may no longer be in correction territory, but there are still some attractive opportunities for long-term investors, especially when it comes to dividend stocks.  Thanks to persistently high interest rates and low expectations for continued rate cuts in the near term, some excellent high-dividend stocks are trading for attractive valuations right now.  With that in mind, here are three stocks, all of which have dividend yields over 4%, that could be worth a closer look right now.
